India Open Women's Tennis Tournament 2014 finale held at Khar Gymkhana in Mumbai, on Sunday, March 23rd, 2014.

 

The '3 Idiots' actor extended his support to the sport and said, "I love the game very much and dreams craft has started this tournament and we all should support this".

 

"We wish this tournament grows and good players come and participate in this and we all get a chance to see them play", the 'Talaash' star added.

Khan, who is a former national level tennis player, was also seen showing his tennis skills after the match. (Bollywood Country Report)
